data.name: Label3.Text
data.value: Yuuri Shibuya is just a normal Japanese high school kid who likes baseball and has a strong sense of justice. One day he sees a former classmate of his, Ken Murata being bullied but when he goes in to stop them they grab him instead and he gets his head dunked in a toilet by the bullies. When his head enters the water, he is sucked into the toilet, and ends up in another world. Waking on dry land, he initially assumes that he is at a theme park, because of the medieval-style clothes the inhabitants wear.
